data.description: Spacious 3/2 with separate dining room, office, and screened-in back porch, huge laundry room and 2-car garage on an acre+ lot. Open floor plan/split floor plan with a cozy living room fireplace. Currently the sellers have his & her offices instead of office and separate dining room since the breakfast room is large enough for dining year-round. The primary suite is large & the attached bathroom features a separate shower, jetted tub, 2 vanities, and lots of natural light. Tall ceilings, lots of closets for additional storage, Roof is 2 years old, NO carpet, security system.
